Package com.fasterxml.jackson.databind

Class DatabindContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.DatabindContext
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DeserializationContext, SerializerProvider
    public abstract class DatabindContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Shared base class for DeserializationContext and SerializerProvider, context objects passed through data-binding process. Designed so that some of implementations can rely on shared aspects like access to secondary contextual objects like type factories or handler instantiators.
    Since:
    2.2

      • resolveSubType

        public JavaType resolveSubType​(JavaType baseType,
                               java.lang.String subClassName)
                        throws JsonMappingException
        Lookup method called when code needs to resolve class name from input; usually simple lookup. Note that unlike resolveAndValidateSubType(com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JavaType, java.lang.String, com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.jsontype.PolymorphicTypeValidator) this method DOES NOT validate subtype against configured PolymorphicTypeValidator: usually because such check has already been made.
        Throws:
        JsonMappingException
        Since:
        2.9
